dc_description_s: These data layers represent trails for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NPortage_Trails_2018.gdbN. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are NPortage_Green_Circle_Trail_2018N, NPortage_Plover_River_Ski_Trails_2018N, and NPortage_Snowmobile_Trails_2018N. [GreenCircle is a vector representation of the Green Circle bicycle/pedestrian trail in Stevens Point, Wisconsin. Most of the trail was mapped using a resource grade GPS. The remainder is traced from airphotos. Recommended use scale is no larger than 1:2400.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
